{"id":61,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":61,"title":"D&C 57","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 57"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, in Zion, Jackson County, Missouri, July 20, 1831. In compliance with the Lord’s command to travel to Missouri, where He would reveal “the land of your inheritance” (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52"},"section 52"],"), the elders had journeyed from Ohio to Missouri’s western border. Joseph Smith contemplated the state of the Lamanites and wondered: “When will the wilderness blossom as the rose? When will Zion be built up in her glory, and where will Thy temple stand, unto which all nations shall come in the last days?” Subsequently he received this revelation."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1-3"},"1–3"],", Independence, Missouri, is the place for the City of Zion and the temple;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.4-7"},"4–7"],", The Saints are to purchase lands and receive inheritances in that area;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.8-16"},"8–16"],", Sidney Gilbert is to establish a store, William W. Phelps is to be a printer, and Oliver Cowdery is to edit material for publication."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1","order":"06.05.057.6835"},["b","1"],"Hearken, O ye elders of my church, saith the Lord your God, who have assembled yourselves together, according to my commandments, in this land, which is the land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Missouri"],", which is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"land"],"which I have appointed and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"consecrated"],"for the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"gathering"],"of the saints."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.2","order":"06.05.057.6836"},["b","2"],"Wherefore, this is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"land of promise"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"place"],"for the city of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.3","order":"06.05.057.6837"},["b","3"],"And thus saith the Lord your God, if you will receive wisdom here is wisdom. Behold, the place which is now called Independence is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"center"],"place; and a spot for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"temple"],"is lying westward, upon a lot which is not far from the courthouse."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.4","order":"06.05.057.6838"},["b","4"],"Wherefore, it is wisdom that the land should be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"purchased"],"by the saints, and also every tract lying westward, even unto the line running directly",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"between Jew and Gentile"],";"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.5","order":"06.05.057.6839"},["b","5"],"And also every tract bordering by the prairies, inasmuch as my disciples are enabled to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"buy"],"lands. Behold, this is wisdom, that they may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"obtain"],"it for an everlasting inheritance."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.6","order":"06.05.057.6840"},["b","6"],"And let my servant Sidney Gilbert stand in the office to which I have appointed him, to receive moneys, to be an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"agent"],"unto the church, to buy land in all the regions round about, inasmuch as can be done in righteousness, and as wisdom shall direct."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.7","order":"06.05.057.6841"},["b","7"],"And let my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Edward Partridge"],"stand in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"office"],"to which I have appointed him, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"divide"],"unto the saints their inheritance, even as I have commanded; and also those whom he has appointed to assist him."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.8","order":"06.05.057.6842"},["b","8"],"And again, verily I say unto you, let my servant Sidney Gilbert plant himself in this place, and establish a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"store"],", that he may sell goods",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"without fraud"],", that he may obtain money to buy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"lands"],"for the good of the saints, and that he may obtain whatsoever things the disciples may need to plant them in their inheritance."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.9","order":"06.05.057.6843"},["b","9"],"And also let my servant Sidney Gilbert obtain a license—behold here is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"wisdom"],", and whoso readeth let him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"understand"],"—that he may send goods also unto the people, even by whom he will as clerks employed in his service;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.10","order":"06.05.057.6844"},["b","10"],"And thus provide for my saints, that my gospel may be preached unto those who sit in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"darkness"],"and in the region and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"shadow of death"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.11","order":"06.05.057.6845"},["b","11"],"And again, verily I say unto you, let my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"William W. Phelps"],"be planted in this place, and be established as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"printer"],"unto the church."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.12","order":"06.05.057.6846"},["b","12"],"And lo, if the world receive his writings—behold here is wisdom—let him obtain whatsoever he can obtain in righteousness, for the good of the saints."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.13","order":"06.05.057.6847"},["b","13"],"And let my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Oliver Cowdery"],"assist him, even as I have commanded, in whatsoever place I shall appoint unto him, to copy, and to correct, and select, that all things may be right before me, as it shall be proved by the Spirit through him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.14","order":"06.05.057.6848"},["b","14"],"And thus let those of whom I have spoken be planted in the land of Zion, as speedily as can be, with their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"families"],", to do those things even as I have spoken."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.15","order":"06.05.057.6849"},["b","15"],"And now concerning the gathering—Let the bishop and the agent make preparations for those families which have been commanded to come to this land, as soon as possible, and plant them in their inheritance."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.16","order":"06.05.057.6850"},["b","16"],"And unto the residue of both elders and members further directions shall be given hereafter. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1a","order":"06.05.057.6851"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.3.3,42"},"D&C 52:3 (3, 42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1b","order":"06.05.057.6853"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.8.7-8"},"D&C 29:8 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.66.64-66"},"45:66 (64–66)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.2.2,42"},"52:2 (2, 42)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1"},"58:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.24"},"103:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1c","order":"06.05.057.6855"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/61.17"},"D&C 61:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.1d","order":"06.05.057.6857"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"},"TG Mission of Latter-day Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.2a","order":"06.05.057.6859"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/48.5"},"D&C 48:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.5.5,42"},"52:5 (5, 42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.2b","order":"06.05.057.6861"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.9"},"D&C 28:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.9.9,62"},"42:9 (9, 62)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.24.22-24"},"103:24 (22–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.2c","order":"06.05.057.6863"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/62.4"},"D&C 62:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/78.3"},"78:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.3a","order":"06.05.057.6865"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/69.6"},"D&C 69:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.3b","order":"06.05.057.6867"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.57"},"D&C 58:57"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.3.3-5,31"},"84:3 (3–5, 31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.10.10-20"},"97:10 (10–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.51.49-51"},"124:51 (49–51)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.4a","order":"06.05.057.6869"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/48.4"},"D&C 48:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jerusalem-new"},"TG Jerusalem, New"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.4b","order":"06.05.057.6871"},["b","4b"],["span.small","IE"],"by metonymy “Jew” here refers to the Lamanites, and “Gentile” to the white settlers."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.5a","order":"06.05.057.6873"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.35"},"D&C 42:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.49.49-51"},"58:49 (49–51)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.70.68-74"},"101:70 (68–74)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.23.22-24"},"103:23 (22–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.5b","order":"06.05.057.6875"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.5"},"Matt. 5:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.20"},"D&C 56:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/59.2"},"59:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lands-of-inheritance"},"TG Lands of Inheritance"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.6a","order":"06.05.057.6877"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.4"},"D&C 53:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.18"},"64:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/70.11"},"70:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.7a","order":"06.05.057.6879"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.24"},"D&C 52:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.14.14,19,24"},"58:14 (14, 19, 24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.7b","order":"06.05.057.6881"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.40.40-41"},"D&C 58:40 (40–41)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/61.7.7-12"},"61:7 (7–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.7c","order":"06.05.057.6883"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/41.9.9-11"},"D&C 41:9 (9–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/51.1.1-20"},"51:1 (1–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.17.14-18"},"58:17 (14–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.8a","order":"06.05.057.6885"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.42"},"D&C 63:42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.26"},"64:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.8b","order":"06.05.057.6887"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.8c","order":"06.05.057.6889"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/48.4"},"D&C 48:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.9a","order":"06.05.057.6891"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/13.18"},"Rev. 13:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.9b","order":"06.05.057.6893"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.15"},"Matt. 24:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.10a","order":"06.05.057.6895"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/4.16"},"Matt. 4:16"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.10b","order":"06.05.057.6897"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/3.5"},"Job 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/23.4"},"Ps. 23:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.11a","order":"06.05.057.6899"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.40"},"D&C 58:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/61.7.7-9"},"61:7 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/70.1"},"70:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.11b","order":"06.05.057.6901"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.37.37,40-41"},"D&C 58:37 (37, 40–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.13a","order":"06.05.057.6903"},["b","13a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/triple-index/cowdery-oliver"},"Index for many references to Oliver Cowdery"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.14a","order":"06.05.057.6905"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family"},"TG Family"],"."]]}
